p=20,width=500,height=500,toolbar=1,resizable=0\u0026#39;); return false;\" title=\"分享 Facebook\"\u003e\u003ci class=\"fab fa-fw fa-facebook\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Facebook\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fmorningspace.github.io%2Ftech%2F2019-plan%2F\" class=\"btn btn--linkedin\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, \u0026#39;window\u0026#39;, \u0026#39;left=20,top=20,width=500,height=500,toolbar=1,resizable=0\u0026#39;); return false;\" title=\"分享 LinkedIn\"\u003e\u003ci class=\"fab fa-fw fa-linkedin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e LinkedIn\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/section\u003e\n\n\n      \n  \u003cnav class=\"pagination\"\u003e\n    \n      \u003ca href=\"/tech/lab/hello-git-cheat-sheet/\" class=\"pagination--pager\" title=\"Hello Git Cheat Sheet\n\"\u003e向前\u003c/a\u003e\n    \n    \n      \u003ca href=\"/tech/elash-and-studio/\" class=\"pagination--pager\" title=\"开源项目Elastic Shell发布暨晴耕工坊栏目上线\n\"\u003e向后\u003c/a\u003e\n    \n  \u003c/nav\u003e\n\n    \u003c/div\u003e",
